      <p id="Par55">The optimum input signal to control the described brain system can be estimated as<sup><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR57">57</xref></sup><disp-formula id="Equ9"><label>9</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M105">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
