				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$W$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M108"><mml:mi>W</mml:mi></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="42003_2021_2133_Article_IEq44.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> is the controllability gramian matrix<sup><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="CR58">58</xref></sup>:<disp-formula id="Equ10"><label>10</label><alternatives><tex-math id="M109">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
